---
import Icon from '@components/ui/Icon.astro';
---
<section class="mt-section-gap max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-12 relative">
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-fixed/20 blur-[100px] -z-10 rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Sekilas Profil Dusun</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant body-lg">
        Berdiri di tepian tebing karang Saptosari, Dusun Bedalo merupakan gerbang menuju
        keasrian alam yang belum banyak terjamah. Kehidupan warga yang harmonis dengan
        ekosistem laut menjadikan kami percontohan desa pesisir lestari.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</span>
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface">Pusat Desa</h5>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Titik kumpul warga dan pusat kegiatan administratif.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/40 text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</span>
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface">Ladang Pertanian</h5>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Lahan subur penghasil palawija dan labu kuning unggulan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</span>
          <div>
            <h5 class="font-bold text-on-surface">Kawasan Pesisir</h5>
            <p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Hingga ke bibir pantai Ngedan dan sekitarnya.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1 relative">
      <div class="w-full aspect-square relative flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 organic-shape bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-fixed/50 to-secondary-container/30"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 w-full p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 relative">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="temple_buddhist" size={32} class="text-primary" />
            </div>
            <div class="h-16 w-0.5 border-l-2 border-dashed border-primary"></div>
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <Icon name="agriculture" size={32} class="text-primary" />
            </div>
            <div class="h-16 w-0.5 border-l-2 border-dashed border-primary"></div>
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary rounded-2xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary">
              <Icon name="beach_access" size={32} />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
